suppressMessages(library("ggplot2"))

读取数据

#读取富集分析表格数据
enrich <- read.delim("enrichment-kegg-sampleid_case-vs-ctrl-Up.xls", head=TRUE, sep="\t", quote="")
#过滤掉小于2个基因的term
enrich <- enrich[which(enrich["ListHits"]>2), ]
#计算P值负log10
enrich$log10p <- -log10(enrich$pval)
#取前20个条目
top20 <- enrich %>% arrange(-log10p) %>% top_n(20,log10p)
#处理一下term名称，显示id
top20[, "term"] <- sub("^path:", "", paste(top20[,1], top20[,2], sep=": "))
#把term设置为因子格式，固定顺序
top20$term = factor(top20$term, levels = rev(unique(top20$term)))

根据数据绘制初步条形图

p1 = ggplot(top20) + geom_bar(aes(y = log10p, x= term ), stat = "identity", width = 0.8) 

p1

设置颜色，设置原点，并调用内置主题theme_classic()

p1 = ggplot(top20) + geom_bar(aes(y = log10p, x= term ), stat = "identity", width = 0.8, fill= "#3361A5") +
     # 设置坐标原点，ggplot2内置的主题theme_classic()
     scale_y_continuous(expand=c(0,0)) + theme_classic()

p1

去掉x轴标题，修改x轴文字方向，并对齐

p1 = ggplot(top20) + geom_bar(aes(y = log10p, x= term ), stat = "identity", width = 0.8, fill= "#3361A5") +
     # 设置坐标原点，ggplot2内置的主题theme_classic()
     scale_y_continuous(expand=c(0,0)) + theme_classic() + 
     theme(axis.title.x = element_blank(), 
           axis.text = element_text(color = "black",size = 10, angle = 90, hjust = 1))

p1

绘制基因数的折线图

p2 = ggplot(top20) +
     geom_point(data = top20, aes(y = ListHits, x= term ),color = "#FFA500",size = 4) +
     geom_line(aes(y = ListHits, x= term , group = 1 ),color = "#FFA500",size=1) +
     # ggplot2内置的主题theme_classic()
     theme_classic() + 
     theme(axis.title.x = element_blank(), 
           axis.text = element_text(color = "black",size = 10, angle = 90, hjust = 1))


p2

组合条形图与折线图，并翻转图片

# 由于整合两种数据，因此对y轴数据需要处理，这里通过2.5倍转换将两个y轴标准进行统一
p1 = ggplot(top20) + geom_bar(aes(y = log10p, x= term ), stat = "identity", width = 0.8, fill= "#3361A5") +
     # 设置两个y轴(sec.axis)
     scale_y_continuous(limits = c(0,3.2),breaks = seq(0,3.2,0.5),expand = c(0,0),name = '-Log10(P value)',
                      sec.axis = sec_axis(~.*2.5, name = 'Term candidate gene number',breaks = seq(0,8,1)))+
     # 添加点线图图层
     geom_point(data = top20, aes(y = ListHits/2.5, x= term ),color = "#FFA500",size = 3) +
     geom_line(aes(y = ListHits/2.5, x= term , group = 1 ),color = "#FFA500",size = 1) + 
     # 翻转xy轴
     coord_flip() +
     # ggplot2内置的主题theme_classic()
     theme_classic() + 
     theme(axis.title.y = element_blank(), 
           axis.text = element_text(color = "black",size = 10, hjust = 1))

p1

p1 = ggplot(top20) + geom_bar(aes(y = log10p, x= term ), stat = "identity", width = 0.8, fill= "#3361A5") +
     scale_y_continuous(limits = c(0,3.2),breaks = seq(0,3.2,0.5),expand = c(0,0),name = '-Log10(P value)',

     geom_point(data = top20, aes(y = ListHits/2.5, x= term ),color = "#FFA500",size = 3) +

     theme_classic() + 
     theme(axis.title.y = element_blank(), 
           axis.text = element_text(color = "black",size = 10, hjust = 1),
           plot.title = element_text(color = 'black',size = 15,hjust = 0.5),

添加图例

p1 = ggplot(top20) + geom_bar(aes(y = log10p, x= term ), stat = "identity", width = 0.8, fill= "#3361A5") +
     scale_y_continuous(limits = c(0,3.2),breaks = seq(0,3.2,0.5),expand = c(0,0),name = '-Log10(P value)',
                      sec.axis = sec_axis(~.*2.5, name = 'Term candidate gene number',breaks = seq(0,8,1)))+
     geom_point(data = top20, aes(y = ListHits/2.5, x= term ),color = "#FFA500",size = 3) +
     geom_line(aes(y = ListHits/2.5, x= term , group = 1 ),color = "#FFA500",size = 1) + coord_flip()+
     theme_classic() + 
     theme(axis.title.y = element_blank(), 
           axis.text.x = element_text(color = "black",size = 10,hjust = 1),
           axis.text.y = element_text(color = "black",size = 9,hjust = 1),
           plot.title = element_text(color = 'black',size = 15,hjust = 0.5),
           axis.title.x = element_text(color = "black",size = 12))

#图例采用手动注释色块、点线以及文字的方式添加

p <- p1 +
  # 蓝色方块
  geom_rect(aes(xmin=1.7,xmax=1.9,ymin=1.7,ymax=1.9),
            fill='#3361A5',color='#3361A5')+
  # 蓝色方块注释文字
  annotate(geom='text',x=1.8,y=2,label='-Log10(P value)',
           size=2.2, hjust = 0)+
  # 橙色线段
  annotate('segment',x=1.2,xend = 1.2,y=1.7,yend = 1.9,
           linetype=1, cex=1,color = "#FFA500")+
  # 橙色点
  annotate('text',x=1.25,y=1.8,label='●',
           size=4,color='#FFA500')+
  # 橙色点线注释文字
  annotate('text',x=1.25,y=2,label='Term candidate gene number',
           size=2.2,hjust = 0)+
  # 标题
  annotate('text',x=18,y=3,label="Case VS Ctrl KEGG Enrichment top 20 (UP)",size=6,angle = -90,hjust = 0)
